Title: gillette Fusion Proglide Power Flexball  Razor(1 Blades)
Description: Introducing Gillette Fusion ProGlide Power Men’s Razor with FlexBall Technology, the razor that responds to contours for Gillette’s best shave. And our best blades are now 2X preferred when used with the Fusion ProGlide handle with FlexBall Technology (overall preference vs. former ProGlide, among ProGlide users). The Fusion ProGlide Power on-board battery delivers soothing Micropulses that help reduce friction and increase razor glide, helping the razor blades move effortlessly so you’ll barely feel them. Reengineered Low Cutting Force Blades feature thinner, finer edges (first 4 blades vs. Fusion) with advanced low-resistance coating to cut effortlessly through hair with less tug and pull than Fusion. A Blade Stabilizer maintains optimal blade spacing for comfort, while allowing the blades to respond to the contours of a man’s face. Plus, the Streamlined Comfort Guard channels excess shaving cream to produce optimal blade contact, stretching the skin for a close, comfortable shave. The innovative MicroComb, exclusive to Fusion ProGlide Power, helps guide stubble to the blades. And the razor’s Enhanced Lubrastrip (vs. Fusion) is infused with mineral oil and lubricating polymers that allow the Gillette Fusion ProGlide Power to move smoothly over skin, even on repeat strokes. Description: FOOT CREAM FootDr TM - Foot Cracks Gone In Double Quick TimeYou feet talk to you in more than one ways. They beg you to give ‘em a little rest and some love. Wondering how? If it’s a cracked heel, they are probably overburdened. If you spot a callus on your feet, they’re asking you not to stand for hours together. And when the calluses turn into painful fissures, your feet are slowly giving up. While age can be one reason your feet are showing these signs, a dry weather, a long hot shower or low humidity levels at home or work can equally make feet unhappy.Meet Ayurgenie Foot Cream, your FOOTDr TM that can reverse the damage naturally! It’s a blend of skin-healing herbal ingredients that are must-haves for an effective foot-care routine. Our skin loves turmeric and this cream has a lot of it. This natural antiseptic keeps feet away from infections and inflammations while soothing cracked heels. Enriched with Almond oil, Jojoba Oil and Kokum butter, this cream hydrates cells, smoothens out flaking skin and gives your feet a velvety-smooth texture. Dry, aching feet need clove oil like how a crying baby needs Mommy – and Ayurgenie Foot Cream contains ample amounts to look after your feet from morning to night. Nature’s best foot-care herbs are blended together with herbal distilled water, making this cream an everyday essential for those who love their feet. Dab a small amount of cream on the heels, between toes and all over the feet. Use it whenever needed, but don’t forget using it after bath and before bedtime everyday for best results.
